Package org.hibernate.ogm.compensation.operation

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CreateAssociationWithKey
    Represents one execution of GridDialect.createAssociation(org.hibernate.ogm.model.key.spi.AssociationKey, org.hibernate.ogm.dialect.spi.AssociationContext) .
    CreateTuple
    Represents one execution of IdentityColumnAwareGridDialect.createTuple(EntityKeyMetadata, org.hibernate.ogm.dialect.spi.OperationContext).
    CreateTupleWithKey
    Represents one execution of GridDialect.createTuple(EntityKey, org.hibernate.ogm.dialect.spi.OperationContext).
    ExecuteBatch
    Represents one execution of BatchableGridDialect.executeBatch(org.hibernate.ogm.dialect.batch.spi.OperationsQueue).
    FlushPendingOperations
    Represents one execution of GroupingByEntityDialect.flushPendingOperations(org.hibernate.ogm.model.key.spi.EntityKey, org.hibernate.ogm.dialect.spi.TupleContext).
    GridDialectOperation
    Represents the execution of one specific method of the GridDialect contract or its optional facets such as OptimisticLockingAwareGridDialect.
    InsertOrUpdateAssociation
    Represents one execution of GridDialect.insertOrUpdateAssociation(AssociationKey, Association, org.hibernate.ogm.dialect.spi.AssociationContext).
    InsertOrUpdateTuple
    Represents one execution of GridDialect.insertOrUpdateTuple(EntityKey, TuplePointer, org.hibernate.ogm.dialect.spi.TupleContext).
    InsertTuple
    Represents one execution of IdentityColumnAwareGridDialect.insertTuple(EntityKeyMetadata, Tuple, org.hibernate.ogm.dialect.spi.TupleContext).
    RemoveAssociation
    Represents one execution of GridDialect.removeAssociation(AssociationKey, org.hibernate.ogm.dialect.spi.AssociationContext).
    RemoveTuple
    Represents one execution of GridDialect.removeTuple(EntityKey, org.hibernate.ogm.dialect.spi.TupleContext).
    RemoveTupleWithOptimisticLock
    Represents one execution of OptimisticLockingAwareGridDialect.removeTupleWithOptimisticLock(EntityKey, Tuple, org.hibernate.ogm.dialect.spi.TupleContext)
    UpdateTupleWithOptimisticLock
    Represents one execution of OptimisticLockingAwareGridDialect.updateTupleWithOptimisticLock(EntityKey, Tuple, Tuple, org.hibernate.ogm.dialect.spi.TupleContext)
